{"about_the_game":"<strong>Hero Survival</strong> is a roguelite game in which you will slay hordes of enemies from classic horror movies by enhancing your character, learning different skills and matching your play style with equipment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Try to survive hordes of enemies</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/play_8_800.gif?t=1722467165\" /><br><br>Face hundreds of classic horror monsters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A very strange company of weirdos to play as</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/battle_gif_3_600.gif?t=1722467165\" /><br><br>Spend the coins earned in each run to unlock new characters. Get stronger, destroy thousands of enemies, survive wave after wave and try not to upset the Mad Time God!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Try out different builds in each run</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/some_6.gif?t=1722467165\" /><br><br>Choose a unique way for your character. Want to freeze your enemies? That's the cryomancer's way for you! Or would you rather play the role of a bomber who blows things up? Or maybe you're ready to rely only on your trusty weapon? Then you are a natural born gunslinger!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A lot of weapons and items to enhance your hero</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/play_9_800.gif?t=1722467165\" /><br><br>Guns? Revolvers? Shotguns? Sniper rifles? Grenade launchers? Automatic rifles? Machine guns? We have them all!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 14 different weapons, from ordinary revolvers and submachine guns to legendary sniper rifles and grenade launchers<br></li><li> Dozens of different skills<br></li><li> Hundreds of item combinations to enhance your character<br></li><li> Your enemies are vampires, werewolves, mummies and other monsters from classic horror movies<br></li><li> Fast-paced runs<br></li><li> Waves of enemies, each one longer and fiercer than the last. How long will you last?</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Apprentice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/f1fa2e602bf5bb9226fdaf1a21e7bd9a6c808b6c.jpg"},{"name":"Student","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/171a305f1b2961b37056d7523771f98f24772666.jpg"},{"name":"Magister","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/f03b37b5a22beced5a4e98cf128261bcdb8df882.jpg"},{"name":"Professor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/2714bbcfc8f2f9c1fc413a1ff91bdc20f4262298.jpg"},{"name":"Newbie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/2bfba90810dadde9acb0898e4ae246ce6eac9866.jpg"},{"name":"Skilled","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/de1255323c3dc0c6dc3f0a18001c2dbc20e1005a.jpg"},{"name":"Savvy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/747be6966e185ed2116ba645a4853413684c6a66.jpg"},{"name":"Killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/5decccb02de4a5c03d553456168c95fe685b5780.jpg"},{"name":"Serial Killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/5a7b515edaf6077cb634f1c6dd99c33f48295a29.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2247620/544d7f0c41624d9625c6cf8bb195efeda840c616.jpg"}],"total":23},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1722467165","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/22